---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-pine mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: December 2025</p>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          GoodChristmasIdeas.com is a participant in affiliate programs and collects minimal information
          necessary to provide our gift recommendation services. We do not require account creation or
          collect personal information directly.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Automatically Collected Information:</strong> When you visit our site, we may collect
          standard web log information including your IP address, browser type, referring pages, and
          pages visited. This information is used for site analytics and improvement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>
          We use cookies and similar technologies to improve your browsing experience and to understand
          how visitors use our site.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Affiliate Cookies:</strong> When you click on product links, our affiliate partners
          (including Amazon) may place cookies on your device to track referrals. These cookies are
          governed by the respective affiliate program's privacy policies.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Analytics:</strong> We may use analytics services to understand site usage patterns.
          These services may collect information about your visits to our site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Amazon Associates Program</h2>
        <p>
          GoodChristmasIdeas.com is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an
          affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees
          by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
        </p>
        <p>
          Amazon may collect information when you click on links to their site. Please review
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=468496" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a>
          for more information about their data practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our site contains links to third-party websites, including retailer sites. We are not
          responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to review
          the privacy policies of any site you visit.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Improve our website and gift recommendations</li>
          <li>Analyze site usage and trends</li>
          <li>Ensure the security of our site</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal information, including
          the right to access, correct, or delete data we hold about you. Since we collect minimal
          personal information, there may be limited data available.
        </p>
        <p>
          To exercise any rights or ask questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at
          the address provided on our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
          information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a
          child under 13, please contact us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this page
          with an updated revision date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please visit our
          <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
